{"tid":518352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益，比著你會點做","createTime":"2018-01-03T08:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T09:11:51.000Z","uid":162644,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2bd1a0fe4db98297292342c2dc857dc43a7d6e","tid":518352,"uid":162644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:40:01.000Z","msg":"件事發生係我朋友身上<br />\n話說佢知道左佢呀哥take野都一段時間<br />\n一直話會戒但都係拖黎拖去<br />\n而父母都知道左，<br />\n但佢地立場係呀哥好辛苦架啦唔好再迫佢<br />\n有日離譜到，問我朋友借架車原來自己做埋拆家做買賣<br />\n當然我朋友更係即刻收番條車匙<br />\n比著係你呢個情況你會點決擇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 報警<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搬出去無眼睇乾淨"},{"pid":"5b9e41e75fd598efd2b7fb53081bbaca4ca0b0a1","tid":518352,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"搬啦"},{"pid":"eaf4f73b7a7263822af02788bdc79a59d972f2da","tid":518352,"uid":162644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b9e41e75fd598efd2b7fb53081bbaca4ca0b0a1","tid":518352,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"搬啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:11:51.000Z","msg":"如果搬我朋友就要賣車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}